--[[ 
These are the hats which you can use for the gui 
(you dont need all of them you use them one at a time)
https://www.roblox.com/catalog/16157957/Bandit-the-Bumbling-Puppy
https://www.roblox.com/catalog/4131662188/Felipe
https://www.roblox.com/catalog/5410382371/Ginger-Kitty-Covering-your-Eyes
https://www.roblox.com/catalog/155675806/True-Pirate-Parrot

There are the controls for the gui
 Y - Make it push you (Need to be wearing another hat in extra)
 E - Make it follow you
 G - Make it go on top of your head
 J - Make the pet do a sound
 K - Make it stay where its at
]]--
